{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Cases forbidden by design","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange Compact","anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradio"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Radio button is a UI element that allows to select a single option from a set of mutually exclusive choices."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Radio button that does not show icon or text, provides greater flexibility when creating other components that require a Radio button to be displayed."}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","platforms":[{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","unavailable":false,"name":"iOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"name":"macOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"16.0","unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS"},{"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"11.0","unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSRadio"},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isEr